Gravity,is,a,website,personalization,service,that,enables,users,to,deliver,unique,recommendations,to,each,site,visitor,based,on,their,interests,or,to,provide,each,visitor,with,a,customizable,homepage,Gravity,can,be,added,to,a,site,simply,by,cutting,and,pasting,a,few,lines,of,JavaScript,and,deciding,what,the,personalized,module,should,look,like,Gravity,Personalization,can,be,used,for,websites,mobile,apps,tablet,apps,or,any,web,connected,services